    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Abilità",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_6571257542853270456.png",
                "id": "talent63980",
                "key": "Favonius Bladework - Maid",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Favonius Bladework - Maid"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Geo DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Full Plate</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Full Plate</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br>Grant 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shield points</span> to your active character.<br>Before this <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shield </span>is fully consumed, the <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> you take is halved.</p><p>(The figure will be rounded up)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/b1d7ce40985ba00be1cddb9ab8853acc_8645088561165242874.png",
                "id": "talent70640",
                "key": "Breastplate",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Breastplate"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Geo DMG</span>. This character gains <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Sweeping Time</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Sweeping Time</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br>When your character uses a Normal Attack: Consume 1 less Geo Die. (Once per Round)<br>Character's <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Normal Attacks</span> deal +2 DMG and their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt is converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/41a3e6172eedfcebb93941683385e926_7017724739086859163.png",
                "id": "talent77267",
                "key": "Sweeping Time",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Sweeping Time"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/05/25750596/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_2738688545419338196.png",
                "id": "talent60989",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Shield</span></strong></p><p>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds) </span>-1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_4042758391368888272.png",
                "id": "talent36749",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
